  "keyFeatures": [
    "Trait-based pluggable architecture for all subsystems",
    "22+ AI provider integrations with custom endpoint support",
    "8+ messaging channel integrations (Telegram, Discord, WhatsApp, etc.)",
    "Hybrid memory system with vector + keyword search",
    "Secure sandbox execution with Docker and native runtimes",
    "AIEOS v1.1 identity standard support",
    "Ultra-lightweight Rust runtime (<5MB, <10ms startup)",
    "Autonomous daemon mode for long-running workflows"
